		<div class="card">
			<div class="card-body">
				<h5 class="card-title mb-3">2020/12/27 - Release 1.7 (We're not dead!)</h5>
				<ul>
					<li class="mb-3">
						Merry Christmas and a Happy New Year! Things are moving slow but we're not dead (yet).
					</li>
					<li class="mb-3">
						For anyone contributing prompts, there is now a profile page. From here you can update your username/password, as well as also quickly view and edit all the prompts you've made. More changes to follow in the new year.
